            <li><b>LA dental cluster</b> — Beverly Hills + WeHo + Pasadena dental corridor Miele Professional standard</li>
            <li><b>Alabama plant late 2025</b> — Miele's first US manufacturing will improve parts lead times</li>
          </ul>
        </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>Licensed · Insured</span>
      <span>Same-day · 5 SoCal counties</span>
      <span>$120 commercial diagnostic · waived with repair</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Miele Professional — separate division from residential Miele</h2>
      <p>
        Miele Group is a German family-owned company, founded by Carl Miele and Reinhard Zinkann in Gütersloh,
        Germany in 1899. The Miele and Zinkann families still own and run the company today, 126 years later. It's
        one of the few major household-appliance brands that has remained family-owned continuously from founding.
        The company operates two related-but-distinct product divisions: residential Miele (household appliances)
        and Miele Professional (commercial and laboratory equipment).
      </p>
      <p>
        The disambiguation that makes this page necessary: <b>residential Miele's product line uses the G series</b>
        naming convention (G 5000, G 7000, etc. for residential dishwashers). <b>Miele Professional uses the PG
        series</b> (PG 8000, PG 8500, PG 8600 for commercial dishwashers). G-series parts are NOT interchangeable
        with PG-series parts. Service technicians trained on residential G-series machines are not automatically
        trained on Professional PG-series equipment. If you're ordering parts or scheduling service, specify "Miele
        Professional" or reference the PG prefix so you're routed to the commercial catalog.
      </p>
      <p>
        Miele is also opening its first US manufacturing plant in Shelby County, Alabama, with production starting
        late 2025. This is a significant moment for US-based Miele parts supply — previously all Miele parts
        sourced from Germany or Miele's US parts warehouse in Princeton, New Jersey. US manufacturing should
        improve LA parts lead times meaningfully once the Alabama operation ramps to full production. For now,
        specialty PG parts remain in the 5-to-10-business-day window from Germany or the Princeton warehouse.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Miele Professional lines we service</h2>
      <div class="model-grid">
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>PG 8000 / PG 8500 / PG 8600 — commercial dishwasher</h3>
          <p>Miele Professional's commercial dishwasher product line. PG 8000 entry-tier undercounter/door; PG 8500
            mid-range; PG 8600 higher-capacity for commercial operations and professional-kitchen mid-volume work.
            Used in LA small-to-mid commercial operations, dental practices (PG 8000/8500 common), and laboratory
            support operations. Service: door gasket, door switch, fill valve, rinse-arm bearing, dosing pumps,
            wash pump rebuild.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>ProfiLine — small business</h3>
          <p>Miele Professional's small-business line — sized for small restaurants, professional offices, smaller
            medical practices. Positions between residential and full commercial PG, designed for heavier-duty use
            than residential Miele can handle but at lower throughput than PG 8500+ machines. Common in LA
            small-business accounts and professional-office kitchens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Mielabor — laboratory / medical / dental (awareness only)</h3>
          <p>Mielabor is Miele Professional's sterile-processing equipment line for laboratories, hospitals, and
            dental practices — washer-disinfectors, glassware washers, specialized instrument-cleaning equipment.
            This is a separate product family from PG commercial dishwashers. Our scope on this page is PG
            commercial dishwashers; Mielabor service is specialized and we coordinate with facility-specific
            requirements on those installations. Call us to discuss Mielabor service options.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>PW / PT Professional laundry (awareness)</h3>
          <p>Miele Professional also makes commercial laundry equipment (PW washer and PT dryer series). Outside
            this page's dishwasher scope but worth knowing that LA dental practices, medical offices, and smaller
            commercial laundry operations often pair Miele PG dishwashers with Miele PW/PT laundry. We service
            both within our commercial scope when the installations are co-located.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>LA dental practice cluster — where PG 8000 and 8500 earn their premium</h2>
      <p>
        Miele Professional's most visible LA presence is the dental-practice cluster. Beverly Hills' dental row
        along Wilshire Boulevard, West Hollywood cosmetic dental practices, and Pasadena family dentistry and
        specialty practices run Miele Professional PG 8000 and PG 8500 machines extensively. The reason is
        engineering specification: PG series machines are engineered to meet sterile-processing workflow
        requirements that standard commercial dishwashers can't match. Temperature logging, cycle-parameter
        documentation, specialized rinse-chemistry integration, dedicated sterile-output cycle modes — all
        features that matter in a dental practice but are irrelevant in a typical restaurant kitchen.
      </p>
      <p>
        Service at dental practices includes specific documentation requirements. California Department of Public
        Health (CDPH) sterile-processing inspection compliance requires documented equipment service records and
        cycle-parameter verification. We provide service documentation appropriate for these dental-practice
        compliance requirements. Beyond the major cluster in BH/WeHo/Pasadena, Miele Professional also shows up at
        Westside dental corridor practices serving the UCLA-adjacent area and at many specialty practices
        throughout the LA basin where PG engineering is specified at install.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>LA laboratory, medical, and biotech cluster</h2>
      <p>
        LA's research-university and biotech cluster is the secondary Miele Professional market. UCLA's research
        laboratories, USC's Keck School of Medicine research facilities, Cedars-Sinai's research labs, the Keck
        Graduate Institute, Caltech-affiliated biotech operations, and the growing LA biotech industrial cluster
        (Pasadena-adjacent biotech corridor, Culver City's emerging biotech presence) run Mielabor laboratory
        equipment alongside PG commercial dishwashers where the installation mixes both uses.
      </p>
      <p>
        Service at research labs and biotech facilities has stringent documentation and sometimes specialty-training
        requirements that we coordinate case-by-case. For straightforward PG commercial-dishwasher service in
        adjacent support operations (cafeteria kitchens, break-room dishwashers in research buildings), our
        standard commercial-dishwasher service approach applies. For Mielabor sterile-processing equipment, we
        coordinate with facility-specific requirements and defer to specialized Mielabor service paths where the
        installation demands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Alabama plant late 2025 — US manufacturing milestone</h2>
      <p>
        Miele is opening its first US manufacturing plant in Shelby County, Alabama, with production starting in
        late 2025. For the Miele brand's 126-year history, this is the company's first manufacturing operation
        outside Europe — a significant investment that signals Miele's commitment to the US market across both
        residential and Professional divisions. For LA operators, the practical implication is potential
        improvement in US parts availability and lead times once the Alabama operation ramps to full production.
      </p>
      <p>
        Current Miele Professional parts supply sources from Germany's Gütersloh and Miele's US parts warehouse
        in Princeton, New Jersey. Typical LA parts lead time: 5–10 business days on specialty PG components, 2–5
        days on common parts (door gaskets, basic fill valves, standard wear items) when they're stocked in
        Princeton. The Alabama plant should shift more of this supply to US-manufactured, which could compress
        lead times meaningfully depending on which part categories Alabama prioritizes. We'll update our service
        expectations as Alabama production ramps — expect initial impact through 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>What Miele Professional repair typically costs</h2>
      <p>$120 flat commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. Typical PG service ranges:</p>
      <table class="price-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Repair</th><th>Typical range (parts + labor)</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Door gasket replacement</td><td>$200–$360</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Door switch / microswitch</td><td>$180–$280</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fill valve</td><td>$240–$400</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Thermostat replacement</td><td>$220–$360</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Rinse-arm bearing</td><td>$220–$380</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Drain pump replacement</td><td>$340–$520</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Rinse booster heating element</td><td>$400–$640</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Wash pump seal kit</td><td>$420–$680</td></tr>
          <tr><td>PG specialty chemistry-dosing module</td><td>$400–$720</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Wash pump rebuild</td><td>$560–$900</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Control board replacement</td><td>$850–$1,450</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Most PG-series calls land $420–$900 parts-and-labor. Miele Professional pricing runs at the higher end of
        the German-premium tier alongside Winterhalter specialty parts due to Germany-sourced parts supply.
        Dental-practice service includes sterile-processing documentation with no parts-pricing premium. Full
        cross-brand context in our <a href="/price-list/commercial-dishwasher-repair-cost/">commercial dishwasher
        repair pricing guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related Miele Professional and residential Miele pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/miele/"><b>Miele brand hub</b></a> — Miele Group family-ownership context, residential-plus-Professional overview</li>
        <li><a href="/brands/miele-dishwasher-repair/">Miele residential dishwasher repair Los Angeles</a> — G-series residential (distinct from Professional PG)</li>
        <li><a href="/brands/winterhalter-dishwasher-repair/">Winterhalter commercial dishwasher repair Los Angeles</a> — German premium peer, family-owned</li>
        <li><a href="/brands/meiko-dishwasher-repair/">Meiko commercial dishwasher repair Los Angeles</a> — German premium peer with US subsidiary</li>
        <li><a href="/brands/electrolux-professional-dishwasher-repair/">Electrolux Professional commercial dishwasher repair Los Angeles</a> — European peer, institutional focus</li>
        <li><a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/">All commercial dishwasher repair in Los Angeles →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/price-list/commercial-dishwasher-repair-cost/">Commercial dishwasher repair cost guide →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Miele Professional dishwasher repair — frequently asked</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <details class="faq">
          <summary>{f.q}</summary>
          <p>{f.a}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Miele Professional dishwasher down? Call the branch nearest your kitchen.</h2>
      <p>Same-day in LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="float-call" aria-label="Call now">☎ Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
</Layout>

